claimFees(uint256).details: Transfers accrued fees of DBXENFT to its owner.

claimXen(uint256).details: Given a DBXENFT, claim the Xen rewards of the underlying XENFT and direct them to its owner. Not permitted during entry cycle of DBXENFT. In doing so, the base power of the DBXENFT will become 1(unless it's already smaller) and the DBXENFT total power is updated according to the new base power and the existent DXN stake.

getCurrentCycle().details: Returns the index of the cycle at the current block time.

mintDBXENFT(uint256).details: Locks an owned XENFT inside this contract and mints a DBXENFT. Must pay a protocol fee based on the estimated Xen rewards the XENFT yields at the time of locking. The estimated Xen also determines the entry power that will provide the DBXENFT a base power from the reward power pool split to all the DBXENFTs created during the cycle. If the XENFT is already redeemed, a DBXENFT that does not take part in the auction of the cycle's reward power nor does it start it is minted and is assigned the base power of 1.

params.xenftId: id of the XENFT to be locked.

stake(uint256,uint256).details: Stake an amount of DXN for the given DBXENFT to give it extra power. Must pay a protocol fee of 0.001 native coin for each DXN. The corresponding DXN is locked until the end of the next cycle.

params.amount: amount of DXN to be staked.

unstake(uint256,uint256).details: Unstake an amount of DXN for the given DBXENFT applying a power decrease to the current cycle if it's an active one or beginning with the next active one. Can only withdraw DXN that has completed the corresponding cycle lock-up.

params.amount: amount of DXN to be unstaked.

BASE_XEN().notice: Helper constant used in calculating the fee for locking XENFT.

MAX_PENALTY_PCT().notice: Upper percentage limit that can be applied as penalty.

SCALING_FACTOR().notice: Used to minimize division remainder when earned fees are calculated.

SECONDS_IN_DAY().notice: Amount of seconds in a day.

baseDBXeNFTPower(uint256).notice: Base power of DBXENFT obtained from the share of power reward of its entry cycle.

currentCycle().notice: Index (0-based) of the current cycle.  Updated upon cycle setup that is triggered by contract interaction  (account burn tokens, claims fees, claims rewards, stakes or unstakes).

currentCycleReward().notice: Power reward amount allocated for the current cycle.

currentStartedCycle().notice: Helper variable to store the index of the last active cycle.

cycleAccruedFees(uint256).notice: The total amount of accrued fees per cycle.

cycleFeesPerPowerSummed(uint256).notice: Sum of previous total cycle accrued fees divided by total DBXENFT powers.

dbxenftAccruedFees(uint256).notice: DXN amount a DBXENFT has staked and is locked during given cycle.

dbxenftEntryPower(uint256).notice: Entry power(in est. Xen reward) of the given DBXENFT.

dbxenftEntryPowerWithStake(uint256).notice: Total entry power(in est. Xen reward) of all DBXENFTs that staked during entry cycle.

dbxenftFirstStake(uint256).notice: Cycle in which a DBXENFT's staked DXN is locked and begins generating fees.

dbxenftPower(uint256).notice: Power of DBXENFT counting towards the share of protocol fees. Equal to base DBXENFT power + (base DBXENFT power * DXN staked) / 100;

dbxenftSecondStake(uint256).notice: Same as dbxenftFirstStake, but stores the second stake separately  in case DXN is staked for the DBXENFT in two consecutive active cycles.

dbxenftStakeCycle(uint256,uint256).notice: DXN amount a DBXENFT has staked and is locked during given cycle.

dbxenftWithdrawableStake(uint256).notice: DXN amount a DBXENFT can currently withdraw.

i_initialTimestamp().notice: Contract creation timestamp. Initialized in constructor.

i_periodDuration().notice: Length of a fee distribution cycle. Initialized in constructor to 1 day.

lastCycleReward().notice: Power reward amount allocated for the previous cycle.

lastFeeUpdateCycle(uint256).notice: DXN amount a DBXENFT has staked and is locked during given cycle.

lastStartedCycle().notice: Stores the index of the penultimate active cycle plus one.

pendingDXN(uint256).notice: Pending staked DXN helper variable used for updating DBXENFT with the corresponding power.

pendingFees().notice: Pending fees added into the pool of the next active cycle.

pendingPower().notice: Pending extra power from DXN staking added into the pool of the next active cycle.

pendingStakeWithdrawal().notice: Pending power decrease applied at the start of the next active cycle.

previousStartedCycle().notice: Stores the index of the penultimate active cycle plus one.

rewardPerCycle(uint256).notice: Total power rewards allocated per cycle.

summedCyclePowers(uint256).notice: Stores the sum of the total DBXENFT powers from all the previous cycles + the current power reward of the given cycle.

tokenEntryCycle(uint256).notice: Cycle in which the given DBXENFT was minted.

totalEntryPowerPerCycle(uint256).notice: Total entry power(in est. Xen reward) in the given cycle.

totalExtraEntryPower(uint256).notice: Updated when staking DXN - used in the calculation of all the extra power that needs to be added to the total power of DBXENFTs.
